          "elements": [
            {
              "id": "ca83c609",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p data-start=\"127\" data-end=\"716\">At Midland Floors, we\u2019re proud to be trusted by leading brands, organizations, and institutions across the DMV. From national retailers and restaurants to healthcare providers, government agencies, and corporate offices, our clients rely on us to deliver commercial floor care that meets the highest standards of quality and durability. Each partnership reflects our commitment to consistency, professionalism, and results that make a lasting impact.</p><p data-start=\"127\" data-end=\"716\">Whether it\u2019s maintaining high-traffic shopping centers, ensuring hygienic conditions in medical environments, or creating professional spaces for offices and agencies, we adapt our services to fit your world. Our goal is simple: keep your floors looking exceptional, safe, and built to last\u2014no matter where your business operates</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2>Diverse Clientele at Midland Floors</h2>\t\t\t\t\n\t\t<p>REI<br />Amtrak<br />Guitar Center<br />Ulta<br />US Renal Care<br />Lego<br />Le Labo<br />Massage Envy<br />European Wax Cente</p><p>Harbor Freight<br />Dept Homeland Security<br />US AID<br />Environmental Protection Agency (EPA)<br />Dept of Labor<br />Lazy Dog Restaurants<br />Raising Cane\u2019s<br />Puma</p><p>Land\u2019s End<br />Famous Footwear<br />Hanes Brand<br />Lacoste<br />Pandora<br />LA Fitness<br />Cava<br />National Park Service<br />National Institute of Health (NIH)</p><p>Wolf Trap<br />At Home Stores<br />CVS<br />Save A Lot<br />Eileen Fisher<br />H&amp;M<br />Barnes &amp; Noble<br />Hallmark</p>\t\t\n\t\t<p style=\"text-align: center;\">REI<br />Amtrak<br />Guitar Center<br />Ulta<br />US Renal Care<br />Lego<br />Le Labo<br />Massage Envy<br />European Wax Cente</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Harbor Freight<br />Dept Homeland Security<br />US AID<br />Environmental Protection Agency (EPA)<br />Dept of Labor<br />Lazy Dog Restaurants<br />Raising Cane\u2019s<br />Puma</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Land\u2019s End<br />Famous Footwear<br />Hanes Brand<br />Lacoste<br />Pandora<br />LA Fitness<br />Cava<br />National Park Service<br />National Institute of Health (NIH)</p>",
                "align": "left",
